{"tha-ap493:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap493:0.2":"Kinkanipupphavagga ","tha-ap493:0.3":"Tikinkanipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap493:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jotantam, ","tha-ap493:1.2":"nisinnam pabbatantare; ","tha-ap493:1.3":"Addasam virajam buddham, ","tha-ap493:1.4":"vipassim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap493:2.1":"Tini kinkanipupphani, ","tha-ap493:2.2":"paggayha abhiropayim; ","tha-ap493:2.3":"Sambuddhamabhipujetva, ","tha-ap493:2.4":"gacchami dakkhinamukho. ","tha-ap493:3.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap493:3.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap493:3.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap493:3.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap493:4.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap493:4.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap493:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap493:4.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap493:5.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap493:5.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap493:5.3":"Nagova bandhanam chetva, ","tha-ap493:5.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap493:6.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap493:6.2":"mama buddhassa santike; ","tha-ap493:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","tha-ap493:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap493:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap493:7.2":"vimokkhapi ca atthime; ","tha-ap493:7.3":"Chalabhinna sacchikata, ","tha-ap493:7.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap493:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma tikinkanipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap493:9.1":"Tikinkanipupphiyattherassapadanam pathamam. "}